  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nOn smoke tests I've noticed that one of nodes was unable to find any bootnodes, trusted nodes or persisted nodes.\r\nBecause of that it struggled a lot to progress during OldHeaders, Forward Sync and later on It wasn't able to proceed well on StateSync.\r\n\r\nAfter restarting it came back to normal, but before that it wasn't able to recover.\r\nWe should investigate a root-cause for such problem and try to prevent or make a mechanism which will automatically try to reconnect to initial nodes.\r\n[Gnosis Peers.zip](https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/files/10002413/Gnosis.Peers.zip)\r\n",
